OL,3,CDriver accused of killing two girls in
OL,4,CWimbledon school crash appears in court
OL,6,FWatch the moment Claire Freemantle
OL,7,Farrives at Westminster Magistrates'
OL,8,FCourt
OL,10,FThe driver of the 4x4 that crashed
OL,11,Finto a primary school and killed two
OL,12,Fyoung girls in 2023 has appeared in
OL,13,Fcourt for the first time, accused of
OL,14,Fcausing death by dangerous driving.
OL,16,FSchoolgirls Nuria Sajjad and Selena
OL,17,FLau, both eight years old, died in the
OL,18,Fincident at The Study Prep school in
OL,19,FWimbledon in July 2023, as the school
OL,20,Fwas celebrating the last day of the
OL,21,Fsummer term.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
