OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781629563
OL,3,CDriver accused of killing two girls in
OL,4,CWimbledon school crash appears in court
OL,6,FClaire Freemantle, 49, faces two
OL,7,Fcharges of causing death by dangerous
OL,8,Fdriving and seven counts of causing
OL,9,Fserious injury by dangerous driving.
OL,11,FAt Westminster Magistrates' Court on
OL,12,FTuesday, Freemantle spoke to confirm
OL,13,Fher identity and was not asked to
OL,14,Fenter any pleas.
OL,16,FShe was allowed to sit behind her
OL,17,Flawyer, rather than in the dock, for
OL,18,Fthe hearing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
