PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781629563
OL,3,CDriver accused of killing two girls in
OL,4,CWimbledon school crash appears in court
OL,6,FShe is accused of killing Nuria and
OL,7,FSelena, as well as causing serious
OL,8,Finjury in the crash to Nuria's mother
OL,9,FSmera Chohan and another mother named
OL,10,FTamsyn Van De Vyver.
OL,12,FA third mother and her seven-month-old
OL,13,Fbaby were also injured, as well as two
OL,14,Feight-year-old girls and a seven-year-
OL,15,Fold girl.
OL,17,FCriminal charges were announced in
OL,18,FMay, after the girls' families
OL,19,Fcriticised the Metropolitan Police for
OL,20,Fits investigation into the crash.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
