PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781629563
OL,3,CDriver accused of killing two girls in
OL,4,CWimbledon school crash appears in court
OL,6,FIn June 2024, Scotland Yard said the
OL,7,Fdriver of the vehicle had suffered an
OL,8,Fepileptic seizure and would face no
OL,9,Fcriminal charges.
OL,11,FBut that decision was reversed, and
OL,12,Fthe Met apologised for the way it
OL,13,Finitially dealt with the incident and
OL,14,Fthe "impact on those affected", adding
OL,15,Fit would be "fundamentally resetting
OL,16,Fhow the Met investigates fatal and
OL,17,Fserious collisions".
