PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1781629563
OL,3,CDriver accused of killing two girls in
OL,4,CWimbledon school crash appears in court
OL,6,FAfter the charges were announced,
OL,7,FFreemantle's lawyers previously said
OL,8,Fshe would plead not guilty to the
OL,9,Fcharges.
OL,11,FSallie Bennett-Jenkins KC, defending,
OL,12,Fasked for Freemantle to be allowed to
OL,13,Fsit in the well of the court, rather
OL,14,Fthan in the dock, due to health
OL,15,Fconcerns.
OL,17,FChief Magistrate Paul Goldspring sent
OL,18,Fthe case to the Old Bailey for a
OL,19,Fhearing on July 14.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
